OL,3,C'Simple' colour card for describing
OL,4,Cbodily fluids could improve patient
OL,5,Coutcomes
OL,7,FA "really simple" tool that makes it
OL,8,Feasier for people to describe the
OL,9,Fcolour of bodily fluids could have a
OL,10,F"huge impact" on patient care,
OL,11,Fresearchers have announced.
OL,13,FA team at Edinburgh Napier University
OL,14,Fhas developed a standardised colour
OL,15,Fpalette that can be used by patients
OL,16,Fand clinicians when describing the
OL,17,Fcolour of fluids like urine and sputum.
OL,26,@oD@COUoD@QO]rD@AOUrD@MO]
