OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F303A1767402403
OL,3,C'Simple' colour card for describing
OL,4,Cbodily fluids could improve patient
OL,5,Coutcomes
OL,7,FThis information can play a key role
OL,8,Fin diagnosing, investigating and
OL,9,Fprescribing for a wide range of
OL,10,Fmedical conditions.
OL,12,FThe free online tool, called What
OL,13,FColour Is It?, resembles a paint
OL,14,Fcolour card, with palettes of either
OL,15,F13 or 15 clinically-relevant colours
OL,16,Ffor identifying the colour of sputum,
OL,17,Furine and faeces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
