OL,7,FThey also said having a chart to refer
OL,8,Fto can reduce the embarrassment that
OL,9,Fcan make it difficult for patients to
OL,10,Fdiscuss bodily fluids with clinicians.
OL,12,FHazel McPhillips, an advanced nurse
OL,13,Fpractitioner and a lecturer at Napier,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We rely on our patients
OL,15,Fdescribing a colour and us assuming
OL,16,Fthat we're thinking the same colour.
OL,18,F"We prescribe, we diagnose, we
OL,19,Finvestigate based on the description
OL,20,Fof that colour, and that's really
OL,21,Fsubjective.
OL,26,@vD@GOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
