OL,3,C'Simple' colour card for describing
OL,4,Cbodily fluids could improve patient
OL,5,Coutcomes
OL,7,F"We know in clinical practice that
OL,8,Fwhenever we look at accidents, there
OL,9,Fare investigations, there are issues,
OL,10,Fit's usually down to poor
OL,11,Fdocumentation or poor communication.
OL,13,F"Almost every fatal accident inquiry
OL,14,Fyou ever look at ends with,
OL,15,F'communication could have been better,
OL,16,Fdocumentation could have been better'.
OL,18,F"This is a very small thing, but if we
OL,19,Fcan standardise that small part, that
OL,20,Fcould have a huge impact on patient
OL,21,Fcare and actually on safety as well."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@eO]
