OL,7,FThe team said the tool could help
OL,8,Fcommunicate accurately during remote
OL,9,Fappointments, such as over NHS24 or
OL,10,Fwhen dialling 111.
OL,12,FThey said a visual chart can also help
OL,13,Fovercome communication barriers due to
OL,14,Ffactors like language, age, and
OL,15,Fcertain medical conditions, which can
OL,16,Fmake it difficult for patients to
OL,17,Fdescribe colours verbally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
