OL,7,FBusiness improvement consultant
OL,8,FStephen Yorkstone explained: "There
OL,9,Fare so many reasons that it's helpful
OL,10,Fto use.
OL,12,F"Kids, for example, might not have the
OL,13,Fsame words for colours that we do,
OL,14,F(likewise) people from different parts
OL,15,Fof the world, or with different
OL,16,Flanguage abilities.
OL,26,@pD@^OUtD@AOU
