OL,3,C'Simple' colour card for describing
OL,4,Cbodily fluids could improve patient
OL,5,Coutcomes
OL,7,F"It's a dead simple website that you
OL,8,Fcan load on your phone, because
OL,9,Fclinical folk use their phones all the
OL,10,Ftime nowadays, and you just click a
OL,11,Fbutton and it opens a colour scale,"
OL,12,Fhe explained.
OL,14,F"You can pull it out of your pocket,
OL,15,Fpoint at a colour so that you can
OL,16,Fcommunicate about colours more clearly
OL,17,Fclinically."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@dO]vD@AOUyD@LO]
