OL,4,Cbodily fluids could improve patient
OL,5,Coutcomes
OL,7,FThe team launched the tool four weeks
OL,8,Fago and, so far, it is being used by
OL,9,Fabout 225 people in a number of
OL,10,Fcountries, in medical specialisms as
OL,11,Fwide-ranging as nursing, physiotherapy
OL,12,Fand dentistry.
OL,14,FMr Yorkstone said: "We know they're
OL,15,Fusing it for about a minute at a time
OL,16,Fand, actually, it takes less than a
OL,17,Fminute to open it, point at the colour
OL,18,Fwith the patient and do that.
OL,20,F"So, we're pretty confident that it's
OL,21,Fstarting to be used.
OL,26,@vD@TOU|D@AOU
