OL,3,C'Simple' colour card for describing
OL,4,Cbodily fluids could improve patient
OL,5,Coutcomes
OL,7,F"And we've got users from across the
OL,8,FUK, America, Norway, Sweden and
OL,9,FAustralia already."
OL,11,FThe team said they hope the tool will
OL,12,Fbecome "a normal part of our
OL,13,Fhealthcare system" used by all
OL,14,Fprofessions across all healthcare
OL,15,Ffields.
OL,17,FMs McPhillips said: "It's going to
OL,18,Fmake so many things so much safer and
OL,19,Fmuch more simple for patients as well
OL,20,Fas staff."
